Invocation Name: italian counter
des:
You can use Italian Counter to have Alexa count for you in Italian!

After you launch the skill, Alexa will ask you to provide a number. Alexa will count up to the number in Italian.

You should provide your number in English. The maximum number accepted is 1,000.

To begin, say, "Alexa, launch Italian Counter!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
